Description: An exceptional blend of contemporary and urban spirit, this S.T. Dupont 58 Avenue Montaigne eau de toilette offers you a woody fragrance. Spicy Notes The eau de toilette is an amalgamation of ambergris accords and essential oils extracted from pepper, clementine, cardamom, sage, bergamot, grapefruit, vetiver and cashmere wood.

Title: Guess EDP - 50 ml(For Women)
Description: Bollinger adorns her flute as she stands in her terrace after a long day’s work, lost in contemplation. She remembers a time when she was just a girl in pigtails, seeing the world through rose-tinted glasses and having a conniption when anybody dared to say happily-ever-afters don’t exist. She laughs at her own naive younger self and appreciates how far she has come in life and mentally measures how much she has achieved and at what cost. She closes the verandah door and goes back inside leaving nothing behind except a trail of Guess. The Eau de Parfum clings to her beguiling curves like no other, becoming part of her in a delicate, subtle way. The celebrated house of Guess presents her with the luxury fragrance the creation of which has been credited to famed perfumer, Maurice Rousel. The opening notes of Guess are topped with the light patter of green apple, luscious wild strawberry, sweet citrusy bergamot and honeyed notes of tangerine. The heart beckons you within with the accords of succulent peach with exotic ylang-ylang, fresh notes of Lily of the Valley, ripe red berries, light zesty magnolia, smooth freesia, jasmine and endearing peony. A heavenly dry down leaves the base redolent with the accords of warm cedar, feathery oakmoss, comforting and powdery musk with smoky resinous amber. The intriguing spice of the perfume lets you dabble with it any time of the day and is presented in a delicately pretty flacon with metal accents forming the trademark letter G through which the naive pink of Guess peeks out. Let the smooth notes of the fragrance lap you up into the eye of its stormy presence as you trudge on along the path less trodden.

Title: LOccitane en Provence Eau de Toilette - 100 ml
Description: Do you know that the perfume you use can add mystery to your personality and give you a sexy appeal? Well, this LOccitane en Provence Eau de Toilette actually can. It celebrates the rugged and bold attitude of modern men, captures you with its sensual fragrance and boosts your passion.  A Seductive Blend of Aromas  This panoramic combination of intense aromas - the oriental note of tonka beans, spiciness of pepper, cinnamon, nutmeg, extract of lavender oil and musk, add a raw depth to the fragrance. The spicy invigorating scents brought together to create this eau de toilette, gives you an undeniable appeal and will attract your peers and colleagues.

Title: Police Pure EDT - 75 ml(For Men)
Description: Modern and complex, Pure from the Italian fashion brand Police reflects a symphonic convergence of divergent elements - a fusion of the past and the present, a reflection of modern man who is sensitive yet impassive. Pure is the elegant essence of a man who is conservative but not conformist, a man who is suave without being slick, a confident man who respects his origins and still looks forward. This luxury perfume creates a fusion of spicy and woody aromas that are emblematic of inherent dichotomies of life as we know it. Uniquely blended, the heady top note of this exhilarating Eau de Toilette opens with accords of incense, ginger and lavender. The spicy heart note invigorates your senses with warm essences of cardamom, patchouli and amber, trailing into an earthy base note cedar wood, rich vanilla and velvety musk. Intensely masculine, Pure from Police is encased in a dark flacon with a lion symbol, emblematic of the mysterious enigma and powerful passions that are hallmarks of the contemporary man. Uniquely Pure, uniquely you.

Title: Aigner White EDT  -  125 ml(For Men)
Description: Etienne Aigner creates White for the man who likes to keep it simple. Everything from his apartment decor to his relationships - he lives by the mantra of minimalism. This luxury Eau de Toilette brings a burst of fragrance to his life without the drama that he detests. It represents who he is and could easily be his signature fragrance. It is a scent that reminds him of a sweet past while accompanying him into a glorious future. White for men brings together spicy sweetness with a feathery yet essential masculine touch. Opening notes with the spicy accords of basil and coriander blend seamlessly with the slightly nutty and sweet cardamom and grapefruit to give the fragrance a mellow yet powerful start. Lily of the Valley takes the heart notes into melon and violet which rest on a base of deep musk, warm resinous amber, vetiver and oakmoss. The classy, rounded white bottle of Etienne Aigner White for Men leaves little to the imagination - pure and straightforward is what you see and that is exactly what you get.

Description: About Flowerchild comb: Flowerchild's wooden combs are one of the gentlest hair grooming tools available. They are prized because each handcrafted comb is really a work of art and wood's capability to condition hair. Wood can absorb the scalp's natural oil, sebum, and spread it through the hair shaft during combing. Maintenance Instruction 1. Like all things great, our combs are fragile and needs love and care. You can use some of the below tactics to keep it happier for longer: 2. Don't use water to clean - wood doesn't react well to water, and may swell and eventually splinter if submerged in water for longer duration. 3. Apply a natural ugg sale oil or wax to some clean cloth. Gently wipe any dirt or debris from the comb, running the cloth through each tine. 4. Use soft bristle brush to work off any stubborn residue the cloth could not remove. 5. Be careful not to scrub too hard. If any residue remains after using the toothbrush, run dental floss or perhaps a string between your tines to get the debris out.

Title: Devinez 100-2006, Cajeput Essential Oil, 100% Pure, Natural & Undiluted(100 ml)
Description: Extracted from the leaves of white wood tree, cajeput oil is manufactured through the process of steam distillation. The tree from which the oil is derived has got pointed leaves, beautiful white flowers and stretchy trunk. The oil is known for its medicinal and therapeutic properties in order to cure various ailments. The health benefits of Cajuput Essential Oil includes its properties as an antiseptic, cosmetic, bactericidal, insecticide, decongestant, analgesic, expectorant, febrifuge, vermifuge, anti-spasmodic, anti-neuralgic, carminative, stimulant, tonic, sudorific, and emenagogue substance. Cajuput essential oil is extracted from the twigs and leaves of the Cajuput tree. The scientific name of the Cajuput tree is Melaleuca Cajuputi. The chief components of Cajuput Oil are Caryophyllene, Alpha Pinene, Beta Pinene, Limonene, Alpha Terpinene, Alpha Terpineol, Gamma Terpinene, Terpinolene, Terpineol, Cineole, Cymene, Linalool, and Myrcene. The process of extracting Cajuput Oil involves steam distillation of its twigs and leaves, which is quite similar to that of extracting Eucalyptus Oil.

The Feather-Light Souffle Matte Morphose Foundation from the house of Loreal Paris will put an end to all your worries. Specially designed to meet the makeup demands of every beauty conscious women, this Loreal Paris Feather-Light Souffle Matte Morphose Foundation brings a great transformation on your face by reducing the imperfections such as pimple marks, fine lines, spots and so on. The texture of this Matte Morphose Foundation is in the form of souffle which is feather-light and can be easily spread across your skin. This Loreal Paris Feather-Light Souffle Matte Morphose Foundation (Golden Honey - 230) when applied gives your skin a matte finish making it perfect for a good makeup. Available in  the shade of Golden Honey, this mousse formula blends perfectly on your skin to add luminousity and glow to your dull skin. Directions for Use Take a required amount of this Feather-Light Souffle Matte Morphose Foundation onto your palm. Spread it evenly all over your face for a neat finish.

Title: L'Oreal Paris Feather - Light Souffle Matte Morphose Foundation(Sable Sand - 240)
Description: It is important to choose a foundation that smoothens your skin tone without making it look made up. Intelligently formulated, this L’Oreal Paris Feather - Light Souffle Matte Morphose Foundation, gives you a perfectly even and smooth tone quite effortlessly. Feathery light and smooth, this foundation blends quite easily on the skin, giving you a perfectly evened out skin tone that looks flawless. With the Sable Sand - 240 shade which looks natural, this foundation certainly helps you steal the show at those dressy occasions by giving you a glamorous look that does not look made up. You will also like the smooth matte finish of this foundation and blends excellently with your skin. You will love the souffle texture of this foundation which feels light; the application of this foundation also helps minimize fine lines so that your skin looks well-toned and radiant. At those glamorous parties, weddings or the dressy occasions at office, this foundation mousse will come in handy to give you a perfect skin tone which will help you make a lasting impression. The matte finish will make sure that your skin looks natural and not made up at all; this foundation is suitable for women.
